OL,5, A US police officer has been fired     
OL,6, after fatally shooting a man in a      
OL,7, motorised wheelchair while responding  
OL,8, to a reported shoplifting.             
OL,10,FTucson police officer Ryan Remington   
OL,11,Ffired nine shots at 61-year-old Richard
OL,12,FLee Richards during the incident.      
OL,14,FThe Arizona city's police chief said on
OL,15,FTuesday that he's "deeply disturbed and
OL,16,Ftroubled" by the officer's actions     
OL,17,Fduring the incident.                   
OL,19,FMr Remington's attorney has defended   
OL,20,Fhis client's actions.                  
